title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-02-2013 MON
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-02-2013 MON



Monday, December 02, 2013
The Knockout Game
 
 

 - 9AM hour

1. Heather MacDonald relates how UCLA has junked Shakespeare, Chaucer, and Milton
 in English Lit. for touchy feely left wing drivel.

2. Time magazine asks convicted leaker of classified military information,
      Bradley Manning what he is thankful for this Thanksgiving. 

3. Mike talks about union demonstrations at Walmart stores on Black Friday.




 - 10AM hour

Money Monday with financial expert, Jordan Goodman.




 - 11AM hour

Guest: Colin Flaherty, author of, 
   'White Girl Bleed A Lot': The Return of Racial Violence to America
                                             and How the Media Ignore It."

 A discussion of the knockout game.
